{"tid":1358512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"吊爆運輸處你老味！！！","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:03:42.000Z","uid":240539,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"331e8486885fef615e216ec4a5402eb98d27f336","tid":1358512,"uid":240539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我今日朝早去考車(棍波客貨車)，叫做係考第二次，今次考何文田，<span style=\"color: red;\">考大圈</span><br />\n<br />\n考完之後我覺得自己算揸得唔算差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考完之後等成績， 點知道佢話我丙部唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後我問返師傅，佢話今朝早全部都係考大圈，而且基本上冇人合格</span><br />\n<br />\n先唔講係唔係我哋揸得差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明何文田出名考細圈，點解今朝早全部大多數人考大圈？我師傅都話未見過佢自己學生連續兩日三個人都係考大圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">解釋番:細圈系禁區範圍， 基本上好少車，以前都係經常考呢條路線。而大圈會經過地盤，路邊好多死車，比較少考。</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔知道有冇政治因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唯一已經fact check左嘅事實，有兩個考牌主任係係警察轉過嚟☻☻ dllm"},{"pid":"b30d528aa24acad216781372941145c2842af23e","tid":1358512,"uid":240539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"331e8486885fef615e216ec4a5402eb98d27f336","tid":1358512,"uid":240539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我今日朝早去考車(棍波客貨車)，叫做係考第二次，今次考何文田，<span style=\"color: red;\">考大圈</span><br />\n<br />\n考完之後我覺得自己算揸得唔算差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考完之後等成績， 點知道佢話我丙部唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cl